Description: Parallelized Login Cracker Supporting Numerous Protocols
 THC-Hydra is a fast and flexible login password cracker that
 supports many protocols including HTTP, FTP, SSH, SMB, RDP, and more.
 Designed for security researchers and penetration testers.
